# INVITATION REGISTRY 2.0

# USER ONBOARDING & ACCESS GOVERNANCE CENTER

# UX + FUNCTIONAL REDESIGN

# Desktop + Mobile Optimized

## Objective

Transform the current Invitation Registry from a simple invitation sender into a complete onboarding, access assignment, user provisioning, and activation management center.

The goal is to allow administrators to:

- Invite users quickly
- Assign roles intelligently
- Assign territories
- Assign organizations
- Assign pricing visibility
- Assign AI access
- Track invitation status
- Automate onboarding
- Monitor user activation
- Re-send or modify invitations without friction

The experience must work seamlessly on desktop and mobile.

